00:01:56.230 --> 00:01:57.530
&gt;&gt; David Levithan:
Hello, everybody.

00:01:57.530 --> 00:01:58.830
All right.

00:01:58.830 --> 00:02:00.130
So, first things first.

00:02:00.130 --> 00:02:02.700
So, I apologize if you've
never seen me speak before,

00:02:02.700 --> 00:02:04.400
